## Processing the data

```{r}
library(dplyr)
df = read.table('diabetes.txt', header = TRUE)
mutate_all(df, funs(na_if(.,"")))
df <- droplevels(df)
diabetes_reduced = select(df, -c("id", "bp.2s", "bp.2d"))

```
